on : "Astonishing what money can do for people, isn't it Mr. Conner? Not too much, you know, just more than enough.  Take Tracy for example.  Never a blow that hasn't been softened for her.  Never a blow that won't be softened.  As a matter of fact, they've even changed her shape, she was a dumpy little thing at one time. Only as it happens I'm not interested in myself for the moment. Not interested in yourself?  You're fascinated, Red.  You're far and away your favorite person in the world."~ ~
